    {
        "text": "You want to meet my dog.",
        "start": 578.11,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "You want to meet my dog.",
        "start": 581.35,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I meet your dog?",
        "start": 584.38,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, yeah, but you can't bring your\ncats.",
        "start": 586.83,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "She's a big dog.",
        "start": 591.19,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 596.11,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, sometimes we say \"can.\"",
        "start": 597.34,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "A little more polite -- could.",
        "start": 599.95,
        "duration": 4.87
    },
    {
        "text": "So, maybe to um a stranger, like if you're\nin an office, and you have to sign a paper,",
        "start": 604.82,
        "duration": 13.12
    },
    {
        "text": "you don't have a pen.",
        "start": 617.94,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You see a woman or a man at the desk.",
        "start": 618.94,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "They have a pen.",
        "start": 623.08,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I use your pen, please?",
        "start": 624.3,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "I would be more polite.",
        "start": 626.39,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a stranger.",
        "start": 627.95,
        "duration": 1.06
    },
    {
        "text": "I don't know them.",
        "start": 629.01,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I might switch from \"can\" to \"could,\" and\nI might add \"please.\"",
        "start": 630.01,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I use your pen, please?",
        "start": 634.48,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "At the end or in the middle.",
        "start": 636.81,
        "duration": 3.139
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please use your pen?",
        "start": 639.949,
        "duration": 2.281
    },
    {
        "text": "You could do \"please\" at the end or \"please\"\nin the middle.",
        "start": 642.23,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please?",
        "start": 646.37,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I please?",
        "start": 647.37,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please use your pen?",
        "start": 648.97,
        "duration": 1.684
    },
    {
        "text": "Even with my children, if I know I'm asking\nsomething special, I'll say to my children,",
        "start": 651.722,
        "duration": 5.768
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Can you please go?",
        "start": 657.49,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Could you please go?\"",
        "start": 658.49,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Because I don't want to.",
        "start": 659.49,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Could you please go to the neighbors and\nget some cheese?\"",
        "start": 661.49,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "I'd ask them.",
        "start": 665.089,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "So, the nicer you are, you change the level:\ncan - could and you can add on the \"pleases.\"",
        "start": 666.529,
        "duration": 10.031
    },
    {
        "text": "\"May\" is also used for permission and requests.",
        "start": 676.56,
        "duration": 5.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 682.41,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "And we ask, um, especially when we want to\nbe polite with somebody who has power and",
        "start": 683.67,
        "duration": 7.78
    },
    {
        "text": "authority -- the director, your boss.",
        "start": 691.45,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 693.93,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May I?",
        "start": 694.93,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Very polite.",
        "start": 695.93,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May I?",
        "start": 696.93,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Uh, can you imagine a situation where your\nphone died.",
        "start": 697.93,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "That happens.",
        "start": 701.91,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "You need to make a phone call.",
        "start": 704.07,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe you're at an office, and you know this\nis a very special request.",
        "start": 706.17,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "You say, \"I'm so sorry.",
        "start": 710.89,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "My phone died.",
        "start": 713.38,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "May I please use your phone?",
        "start": 714.88,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please make a phone call?\"",
        "start": 716.81,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "l mean, that's a very special request, but\nyou might need to make it.",
        "start": 718.55,
        "duration": 3.94
    },
    {
        "text": "\"My phone died.",
        "start": 722.49,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "May I please use your phone?",
        "start": 724.13,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "May I please?",
        "start": 726.85,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May I please use your phone?",
        "start": 727.85,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please make a phone call?",
        "start": 730.31,
        "duration": 1.61
    },
    {
        "text": "And you can say, \"It's local, not international.",
        "start": 731.92,
        "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm not calling Brazil.\"",
        "start": 736.26,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, so you're at a hotel, and you're with\nyour husband.",
        "start": 738.44,
        "duration": 6.13
    },
    {
        "text": "They gave you one pillow.",
        "start": 744.57,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "You need another pillow, so you need to pick\nup the phone, and you need to ask for another",
        "start": 747.03,
        "duration": 5.99
    },
    {
        "text": "pillow.",
        "start": 753.02,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "May I have one more pillow, please?",
        "start": 754.11,
        "duration": 7.669
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes.",
        "start": 761.779,
        "duration": 1.101
    },
    {
        "text": "No!",
        "start": 762.88,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes.",
        "start": 763.97,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "So, you're on the phone.",
        "start": 765.07,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "\"May I have another pillow, please?",
        "start": 768.88,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "And you can always give your room number.",
        "start": 771.6,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "This is room 212.",
        "start": 774.34,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "They should know, but, \"This is room 212.",
        "start": 775.42,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "May I have another pillow, please?\"",
        "start": 777.37,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Sure.",
        "start": 780.52,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We'll bring it to you.\"",
        "start": 781.52,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 783.66,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, you're calling a restaurant.",
        "start": 784.66,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a nice restaurant, and you want to make\na reservation for 7 p.m.",
        "start": 786.81,
        "duration": 9.38
    },
    {
        "text": "May I make a reservation to...for...for 6\np.m.? Sure.",
        "start": 796.19,
        "duration": 9.55
    },
    {
        "text": "How many?",
        "start": 805.74,
        "duration": 1.61
    },
    {
        "text": "How many are in your party?",
        "start": 807.35,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "They'll say\" party.\"",
        "start": 808.94,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "How many in your party?",
        "start": 809.95,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Four.",
        "start": 812.05,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Four.",
        "start": 813.05,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 814.05,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May have your... they'll ask, \"May I have\nyour name, please?\"",
        "start": 815.05,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 817.86,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And then they'll take your name.",
        "start": 818.86,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 820.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May I make a reservation, please?",
        "start": 821.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "May I make a reservation for 7 p.m.?",
        "start": 822.36,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "For 6 p.m.? Good.",
        "start": 825.31,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, you're calling a company for some reason.",
        "start": 828.11,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "That happens, and you want to speak to Mr.\nPeterson.",
        "start": 831.87,
        "duration": 4.09
    },
    {
        "text": "One more time.",
        "start": 835.96,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Hello.",
        "start": 838.24,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "ABC Company.",
        "start": 839.24,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, may I speak to Miss...",
        "start": 840.52,
        "duration": 5.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Mr. Peter...Peter, please?",
        "start": 845.84,
        "duration": 6.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Sure.",
        "start": 851.95,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "May I ask who's calling?",
        "start": 853.99,
        "duration": 5.88
    },
    {
        "text": "They'll ask for your name, so the question\nis, \"May I have your name?",
        "start": 859.87,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "May I have your name?\"",
        "start": 862.74,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what you'll hear, and you have to give\nyour name.",
        "start": 864.66,
        "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
        "text": "My first name is Flavia.",
        "start": 869.14,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, so now decide.",
        "start": 871.68,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "We have CAN, COULD, and MAY.",
        "start": 873.75,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "You need to choose for the situation and think,\n\"Who are you talking to?\" Okay?",
        "start": 877.19,
        "duration": 5.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, you want to borrow your friend's sweater.",
        "start": 882.58,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I borrow your sweater?",
        "start": 886.11,
        "duration": 4.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 890.66,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what I'd say.",
        "start": 891.66,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I borrow your sweater?",
        "start": 895.22,
        "duration": 2.21
    },
    {
        "text": "Can she borrow your sweater?",
        "start": 897.43,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes.",
        "start": 899.27,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Sure.",
        "start": 900.55,
        "duration": 1.289
    },
    {
        "text": "No problem.",
        "start": 901.839,
        "duration": 2.581
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, you want to borrow her necklace.",
        "start": 904.42,
        "duration": 5.08
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a nice necklace.",
        "start": 909.5,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I borrow your necklace?",
        "start": 911.47,
        "duration": 5.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 917.0,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's fine, but if it's a very nice necklace,\nI'd be like, \"Can I borrow your necklace,",
        "start": 918.0,
        "duration": 4.42
    },
    {
        "text": "please?",
        "start": 922.42,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please borrow your necklace?\"",
        "start": 923.42,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I borrow your necklace, please?",
        "start": 925.18,
        "duration": 4.85
    },
    {
        "text": "No.",
        "start": 930.03,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "No.",
        "start": 931.05,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just too special.",
        "start": 932.08,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Say, \"Yes, but you have to be very, very careful.\"",
        "start": 933.08,
        "duration": 5.939
    },
    {
        "text": "We use CAN, COULD, and MAY for requests and\npermission.",
        "start": 939.019,
        "duration": 9.601
    },
    {
        "text": "If we need help or if we want to do something,\nwe ask questions with these verbs, these modal",
        "start": 948.62,
        "duration": 7.38
    },
    {
        "text": "verbs.",
        "start": 956.0,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "Repeat after me.",
        "start": 957.27,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I use your pen?",
        "start": 961.05,
        "duration": 5.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Could I please use your pen?",
        "start": 966.69,
        "duration": 7.3
    },
    {
        "text": "May I use your pen, please?",
        "start": 973.99,
        "duration": 6.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you help me?",
        "start": 980.09,
        "duration": 4.29
    },
    {
        "text": "Could you please help me?",
        "start": 984.38,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Could you help me, please?",
        "start": 987.5,
        "duration": 7.91
    },
    {
        "text": "Note how we only use \"May I?\" in a question.",
        "start": 995.41,
        "duration": 3.83
    },
    {
        "text": "We don't say, \"May you?\"",
        "start": 999.24,
        "duration": 5.539
    },
    {
        "text": "It's time for a fun speaking activity.",
        "start": 1004.779,
        "duration": 2.631
    },
    {
        "text": "Listen to Flavia, Andreia, and I create a\nstory.",
        "start": 1007.41,
        "duration": 4.75
    },
    {
        "text": "You can do this too.",
        "start": 1012.16,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Tell a story.",
        "start": 1014.31,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "Use the words you know in English.",
        "start": 1016.04,
        "duration": 2.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Have fun!",
        "start": 1018.57,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, so let's use some of the language:\nborrow and lend.",
        "start": 1019.57,
        "duration": 5.589
    },
    {
        "text": "We can borrow.",
        "start": 1025.159,
        "duration": 1.451
    },
    {
        "text": "We can lend.",
        "start": 1026.61,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna tell a story, and you help me continue\nthe story.",
        "start": 1027.88,
        "duration": 4.37
    },
    {
        "text": "I...I don't have a sister, but this is a story,\nso, um I borrowed my sister's jacket, and",
        "start": 1032.25,
        "duration": 8.621
    },
    {
        "text": "I lost it.",
        "start": 1040.871,
        "duration": 1.389
    },
    {
        "text": "Then what?",
        "start": 1042.26,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "I talked...talked or told?",
        "start": 1043.92,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "I told my my sister that I lost her jacket,\nand she was very angry.",
        "start": 1047.85,
        "duration": 13.97
    },
    {
        "text": "Then what?",
        "start": 1061.82,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "My sister asked me to buy another jacket for\nher, and I told her, \"I have no money.\"",
        "start": 1063.58,
        "duration": 15.49
    },
    {
        "text": "And I cried.",
        "start": 1079.07,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "And then?",
        "start": 1080.22,
        "duration": 6.182
    },
    {
        "text": "If you don't have something, you say, \"Pass.\"",
        "start": 1086.402,
        "duration": 6.448
    },
    {
        "text": "Pass.",
        "start": 1092.85,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, I offered...",
        "start": 1095.15,
        "duration": 6.13
    },
    {
        "text": "I offered, um, a sweater to my sister.",
        "start": 1101.28,
        "duration": 3.029
    },
    {
        "text": "Good idea.",
        "start": 1104.309,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 1105.309,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I went to my closet, I found a sweater, and\nI offered the sweater to my sister.",
        "start": 1106.309,
        "duration": 5.831
    },
    {
        "text": "She accept...she accepted it.",
        "start": 1112.14,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 1113.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 1114.36,
        "duration": 1.199
    },
    {
        "text": "New story and we'll go this way.",
        "start": 1115.559,
        "duration": 5.141
    },
    {
        "text": "Um...",
        "start": 1120.7,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "My car had no gas, so I borrowed my friend's\ncar.",
        "start": 1121.7,
        "duration": 7.63
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 1129.33,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "I crashed my friend's car.",
        "start": 1132.13,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "I cried.",
        "start": 1136.58,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "I cried.",
        "start": 1140.2,
        "duration": 6.182
    },
    {
        "text": "I didn't want to call my friend.",
        "start": 1150.143,
        "duration": 5.11
    },
    {
        "text": "I tried to fix the car",
        "start": 1155.253,
        "duration": 6.807
    },
    {
        "text": "before he, uh, sees it...before he saw it.",
        "start": 1162.06,
        "duration": 6.626
    },
    {
        "text": "He saw.",
        "start": 1168.686,
        "duration": 2.179
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 1170.865,
        "duration": 1.435
    },
    {
        "text": "But my friend called me.",
        "start": 1172.3,
        "duration": 10.557
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hi.",
        "start": 1182.857,
        "duration": 1.63
    },
    {
        "text": "The car is okay?\"",
        "start": 1184.487,
        "duration": 3.928
    },
    {
        "text": "And I cried.",
        "start": 1188.415,
        "duration": 4.293
    },
    {
        "text": "And I confessed.",
        "start": 1195.572,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Good!",
        "start": 1197.962,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "I confessed.",
        "start": 1199.472,
        "duration": 2.553
    },
    {
        "text": "Um, then my friend cried and said or asked,\n\"How bad is it?\"",
        "start": 1202.025,
        "duration": 16.495
    },
    {
        "text": "It's not too bad, but there's a lot scratches.",
        "start": 1218.52,
        "duration": 7.094
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh good.",
